metadata.name: Spotlight
metadata.description:
This is a portrait of a young curious leopard called Jilime, child to the famous Luluka of Maasai Mara. It's always fascinating to see this curious cub and annoying and playing around with her mother. 
Jilime is known for having a character filled with curiosity and boldness. Since he is now transitioning into adulthood, his mother is attempting to leave him on his own so that he can become independent; to explore and survive the opportunities and challenges that are incoming on his journey.
